						<summary>

						<p>This records an endowment in gold of 5 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> realised by the sale of some cows gifted by donors for burning a lamp during the daily services in the temple of Tirumūlaṭṭāṉattu-Perumānaḍigaḷ at Tirunalakkuṉṟam, as it was found difficult to maintain the cows by the temple. (No. 44, <hi rend="italic">Pud. Ins.</hi>, Texts.)</p>						

